data.description: ATTENTION BUYERS SELLER IS WILLING TO CONTRIBUTE TO CLOSING COST. Welcome to 17718 Deodar St. This charming home is centrally located and offers a tremendous opportunity for those seeking a spacious lot to accommodate all your needs and endless possibilities. Fenced and cross fenced.  This home has an open floor-plan, with extra bonus room addition.  Kitchen has plenty of cupboards for storage. Dining area that flows nicely with the living room equipped with a cozy rock fireplace. 3 oversized bedrooms, ceiling fans/w/lights in every room and 2 full bathrooms.
